(70, 'Vitamín B Complex - 90 tabliet', 'OstroVit', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B Complex je v&yacute;živov&yacute; doplnok v&nbsp;tabletovej podobe&nbsp;s obsahom&nbsp;8 vitam&iacute;nov skupiny B,&nbsp;ale aj&nbsp;vitam&iacute;nu C a E.&nbsp;Už&iacute;van&iacute;m B complexu podpor&iacute;te svoju&nbsp;imunitu&nbsp;a cel&uacute; s&eacute;riu&nbsp;procesov vo svojom tele.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B1&nbsp;(tiam&iacute;n) - podporuje&nbsp;l&aacute;tkov&uacute; premenu,&nbsp;fungovanie&nbsp;nervovej s&uacute;stavy, srdca a psychiky.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B2&nbsp;(riboflav&iacute;n) - je prospe&scaron;n&yacute; pre&nbsp;redukciu &uacute;navy&nbsp;a vyčerpania,&nbsp;ochranu buniek pred oxidačn&yacute;m stresom&nbsp;alebo udržanie&nbsp;červen&yacute;ch krviniek.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B3&nbsp;(niac&iacute;n) - podporuje&nbsp;l&aacute;tkov&uacute; premenu,&nbsp;udržanie zdravej&nbsp;pokožky a slizn&iacute;c,&nbsp;ale aj optim&aacute;lnu&nbsp;funkciu nervovej s&uacute;stavy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B5&nbsp;(kyselina pantot&eacute;nov&aacute;) - prispieva k optim&aacute;lnej synt&eacute;ze a l&aacute;tkovej premene&nbsp;vitam&iacute;nu D, steroidn&yacute;ch horm&oacute;nov a ist&yacute;ch neurotransmiterov.&nbsp;Redukuje &uacute;navu&nbsp;a podporuje zdrav&uacute;&nbsp;du&scaron;evn&uacute; v&yacute;konnosť.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B6&nbsp;- je užitočn&yacute; pre spr&aacute;vnu&nbsp;synt&eacute;zu cyste&iacute;nu,&nbsp;produkciu&nbsp;červen&yacute;ch krviniek,&nbsp;l&aacute;tkov&uacute; premenu&nbsp;bielkov&iacute;n a glykog&eacute;nu&nbsp;alebo&nbsp;regul&aacute;ciu hormon&aacute;lnej činnosti.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B7&nbsp;(biot&iacute;n) - prispieva k fungovaniu&nbsp;psychiky,&nbsp;udržaniu zdrav&yacute;ch&nbsp;slizn&iacute;c, vlasov a pokožky,&nbsp;podporuje&nbsp;fungovanie nervov&eacute;ho syst&eacute;mu&nbsp;a&nbsp;l&aacute;tkov&uacute; premenu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B9&nbsp;(kyselina listov&aacute;) - je prospe&scaron;n&aacute; pre&nbsp;tvorbu krvi, synt&eacute;zu aminokysel&iacute;n, podporu rastu z&aacute;rodočn&yacute;ch tkan&iacute;v&nbsp;počas tehotenstva a&nbsp;redukciu &uacute;navy.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n B12&nbsp;- je prospe&scaron;n&yacute; pre&nbsp;fungovanie imunity,&nbsp;tvorbu&nbsp;červen&yacute;ch krviniek,&nbsp;l&aacute;tkov&uacute; premenu&nbsp;homocyste&iacute;nu&nbsp;a optim&aacute;lnu&nbsp;funkciu psychiky.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n C&nbsp;- je užitočn&yacute; pre&nbsp;podporu imunity&nbsp;a ochranu buniek pred&nbsp;oxidačn&yacute;m stresom,&nbsp;zv&yacute;&scaron;enie&nbsp;vstreb&aacute;vania železa,&nbsp;redukciu&nbsp;&uacute;navy&nbsp;a vyčerpania, ale aj&nbsp;tvorbu kolag&eacute;nu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Vitam&iacute;n E&nbsp;- je prospe&scaron;n&yacute; pre&nbsp;ochranu buniek&nbsp;pred&nbsp;oxidačn&yacute;m stresom.</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: #007fff;\"><strong>Vitam&iacute;n B Complex a jeho v&yacute;hody</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>je to komplex 10 vitam&iacute;nov</li>\r\n<li>prispieva k fungovaniu imunity</li>\r\n<li>je užitočn&yacute; pre ochranu buniek pred oxidačn&yacute;m stresom</li>\r\n<li>je užitočn&yacute; pre fungovanie nervovej s&uacute;stavy</li>\r\n<li>podporuje l&aacute;tkov&uacute; premenu&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>podporuje redukciu &uacute;navy a vyčerpania</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: #007fff;\"><strong>Zloženie&nbsp;</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Plniv&aacute;: fosforečnan v&aacute;penat&yacute;, &scaron;krob; Kyselina L-askorbov&aacute; (vitam&iacute;n C), plnidlo: mikrokry&scaron;talick&aacute; celul&oacute;za; Maltodextr&iacute;n, protihrudkuj&uacute;ca l&aacute;tka: oxid kremičit&yacute;; kyselina nikot&iacute;nov&aacute; (niac&iacute;n), DL-alfa-tokoferylacet&aacute;t (vitam&iacute;n E), D-pantoten&aacute;t v&aacute;penat&yacute; (kyselina pantot&eacute;nov&aacute;), protihrudkuj&uacute;ca l&aacute;tka: horečnat&eacute; soli obsahuj&uacute;ce mastn&eacute; kyseliny; pyridox&iacute;n hydrochlorid (vitam&iacute;n B6), riboflav&iacute;n (vitam&iacute;n B2), tiam&iacute;n hydrochlorid (tiam&iacute;n), kysl&yacute; pteroylmonoglutam&aacute;t (kyselina listov&aacute;), D-biot&iacute;n (biot&iacute;n), kyanokobalam&iacute;n (vitam&iacute;n B12).&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: #007fff;\"><strong>D&aacute;vkovanie</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Odpor&uacute;čame už&iacute;vať jednu tabletu denne pred jedlom.&nbsp;</p>', 5.95, 25, ' ', ' ', '2025-05-17 16:01:48', '2025-05-17 16:01:48', 'img/produkty/682896ccea4c96.00042000.webp', ' ', 'Vitamín B Complex sú tablety s obsahom 8 vitamínov skupiny B, obohoatené o vitamín C a E. Ich užívaním podporíte viaceré procesy v organizme, napríklad fungovanie imunity, látkovú premenu alebo redukciu únavy a vyčerpania.', 0),
(71, 'Vitamín C 1000 mg', 'NOW Foods', '<p dir=\"ltr\">Vitam&iacute;n C 1000 mg&nbsp;s&uacute;&nbsp;veg&aacute;nske kapsuly&nbsp;s obsahom až&nbsp;1000 mg vitam&iacute;nu C,&nbsp;doplnen&eacute; o&nbsp;komplex citrusov&yacute;ch bioflavonoidov&nbsp;a flavonoid&nbsp;rut&iacute;n.&nbsp; Jeho pr&iacute;jem prispieva k optim&aacute;lnemu&nbsp;fungovaniu imunity, ľudskej psychiky&nbsp;a ochrane buniek pred&nbsp;oxidačn&yacute;m stresom.&nbsp;Vitam&iacute;n C tiež napom&aacute;ha k&nbsp;redukcii &uacute;navy a vyčerpania&nbsp;a fungovaniu&nbsp;nervov&eacute;ho syst&eacute;mu.&nbsp;Okrem in&eacute;ho,&nbsp;zvy&scaron;uje vstreb&aacute;vanie železa,&nbsp;prispieva k&nbsp;tvorbe kolag&eacute;nu&nbsp;a podieľa sa na optim&aacute;lnom&nbsp;energetickom metabolizme.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color: #007fff;\"><strong>Vitam&iacute;n C 1000 mg a jeho v&yacute;hody</strong></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>obsahuje až 1000 mg vitam&iacute;nu C v d&aacute;vke</li>\r\n<li>je vo forme veg&aacute;nskych kaps&uacute;l</li>\r\n<li>podporuje fungovanie imunitn&eacute;ho a nervov&eacute;ho syst&eacute;mu</li>\r\n<li>prispieva k redukcii &uacute;navy a vyčerpania</li>\r\n<li>podieľa sa na ochrane buniek pred oxidačn&yacute;m stresom</li>\r\n<li>je vhodn&yacute; aj pre veg&aacute;nov a vegetari&aacute;nov</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #007fff;\"><strong>D&aacute;vkovanie</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>Už&iacute;vajte 1 kapsulu denne.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #007fff;\"><strong>Zloženie</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>Hypromel&oacute;za (celul&oacute;zov&aacute; kapsula), kyselina stearov&aacute; (rastlinn&yacute; zdroj), stear&aacute;t horečnat&yacute; (rastlinn&yacute; zdroj) a oxid kremičit&yacute;.</p>', 10.50, 17, ' ', ' ', '2025-05-17 16:03:47', '2025-05-22 09:40:07', 'img/produkty/68289743cf8477.14797176.webp', ' 